.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, baking, drawing, fishing, gardening
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dancingmaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
City: prague, hannover, liverpool, venice, hamburg
1. the british is the person who's hobby is drawing
2. the swedish is the person traveling to liverpool
3. the danish is the person drinking tea
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing
5. the person who's hobby is baking is the person drinking coffee
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the person traveling to hannover
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague
11. the person traveling to hamburgs is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the dancingmaster-smoker is the person drinking beer
13. the german is the prince-smoker
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Hobby		|    gardening	|     dancing	|      drawing	|     baking	|     fishing	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| City		|     prague	|    hamburg	|     hannover	|     venice	|      liverpool	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   dancingmaster	|
